WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:13.560
Detective Chief Inspector Nicola Crooks
 was released from custody today

2
00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:16.360
after the Metropolitan
 Police Cyber Crime Unit

3
00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:20.400
quickly uncovered evidence
 that the incriminating social media posts

4
00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:25.320
were part of an organised attempt
 to discredit the case against APT.

5
00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:29.240
Apparently, the cyber detectives
 were so prompt in their response

6
00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:31.320
and so thorough in their evidence

7
00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:36.000
that the ringleaders of APT pled guilty
 as soon as the new evidence was presented.

8
00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:39.320
It's looking likely
 that the days of APT are numbered.

9
00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:43.040
For more on this story,
 we go to our crime reporter, Will Tellit.

